{
  "Name": "Haz 8x2 SSCPGE | Scout Stationary Clear Practice Non-SP Scout Edition | B03",
  "Description": "
	Update:

	Revert non-stationary enemy count to BO1's.

	=======================================================================================

	Designed specifically for grounded Scout solo stationary-clearing practice.

	Base Settings:

	4-player scaling.
	Based on StoneMason's 8x2.

	Adjustments:

	Adjust enemies rarity.
	First resupply is free; subsequent ones cost 60 Nitra.
	Increase projectile speed to CN Haz 8 level (2.3).
	Nerf Bulk resistance.
	Nerf resistance for large enemies (excluding stationaries).
	Reduce Swarmer cap to 60.
	Reduce spawn counts for all non-stationary enemies.

	Rules:

	Bosco is allowed. 
	Goal is clearing out high-threat stationaries; don't have to finish the mission.
	You can teleport straight into the main cave and start clearing.

	Recommended Mods:

	Custom Mission (so you can manually select the exact mission type you want to practice on).
	Enemy Count (to monitor your clear progress and gauge the room's difficulty).
  ",
